{"sid":"campaign_M1_broken_bridge_name","text":"毀損橋梁"},
{"sid":"campaign_M1_broken_bridge_description","text":"除非修復，否則無法通過。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M1_broken_bridge_narrativeDescription","text":"是誰破壞的？為什麼要破壞？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_shroom_tether_name","text":"束縛"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_shroom_tether_description","text":"彷彿來自異界，蘑菇與根莖的奇異結合體。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_shroom_tether_narrativeDescription","text":"它是從土裡長出來，還是長進土裡的？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_empty_mine_name","text":"空洞礦場"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_empty_mine_description","text":"這些水晶上的鮮紅光芒已褪去。真奇怪……"},
{"sid":"campaign_M2_empty_mine_narrativeDescription","text":"無用的岩石。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_necro_altar_name","text":"不祥祭壇"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_necro_altar_description","text":"致命氣息籠罩此地。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_necro_altar_narrativeDescription","text":"怪異。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_cage_name","text":"牢籠"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_cage_description","text":"數名織光者被囚禁在裡面。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M3_cage_narrativeDescription","text":"這可不妙……"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_burning_man_name","text":"？？？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_burning_man_description","text":"這<b>究竟是</b>何等瘋狂……？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_burning_man_narrativeDescription","text":"他們還……活著？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_construction_site_name","text":"工地"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_construction_site_description","text":"這裡在建造些什麼。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_construction_site_narrativeDescription","text":"難怪精靈們如此激動。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_diary_name","text":"遺忘日記"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_diary_description","text":"閱讀後可能會對這位神祕的旅者有所了解。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_diary_narrativeDescription","text":"不過說實話……偷看行為太可恥了。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_stargazer_tower_name","text":"觀星者之塔"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_stargazer_tower_description","text":"與天空說話的瘋狂觀星者就住在這裡。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M4_stargazer_tower_narrativeDescription","text":"真要說……我們不都有一點瘋癲嗎？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_empty_name","text":"廢棄木棚屋"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_empty_description","text":"一定有某人在這裡住了很長一段時間。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_empty_narrativeDescription","text":"還不錯，稍微布置一下就能帶來生機。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_name","text":"好友之家"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_description","text":"兩縷失落的靈魂終能尋得平靜之處。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M5_death_knight_house_narrativeDescription","text":"有狗狗陪著，一切安好。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_cage_name","text":"牢籠"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_cage_description","text":"瓦倫蒂娜一定被關在裡面。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_cage_narrativeDescription","text":"看見人類大小的牢籠就這樣被丟在那裡，真是令人不安。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_mearea_shrine_name","text":"梅瑞亞聖壇"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_mearea_shrine_description","text":"一座古老的祭壇，上面雕刻著黃金、光明和幸運的象徵。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M6_mearea_shrine_narrativeDescription","text":"祝福你。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_name","text":"死靈術增幅器"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_description","text":"一座充滿黑暗能量的方尖碑。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_narrativeDescription","text":"一項早已被世人遺忘的古老技術。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_destroyed_name","text":"毀壞增幅器"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_destroyed_description","text":"失去了所有能量的廢墟。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_necromancy_amplifier_destroyed_narrativeDescription","text":"每消失一個，不死者大軍就愈加虛弱。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_scientist_house_name","text":"詭異小屋"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_scientist_house_description","text":"適合法師或科學家。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_scientist_house_narrativeDescription","text":"其中有何祕密呢……？"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_sylvan_altar_name","text":"森林祭壇"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_sylvan_altar_description","text":"古老而險惡的建築，令人不斷憶起黑暗時代。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_sylvan_altar_narrativeDescription","text":"有人說這裡的陰影裡仍舊述說著被遺忘的祕密。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_shroom_name","text":"能量蘑菇"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_shroom_description","text":"似乎蘊含著來自異界的奇異能量。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_shroom_narrativeDescription","text":"摸摸看，誰知道會發生什麼事……"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_name","text":"菌絲體殘骸"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_description","text":"如果站得夠近，幾乎就能聽到微弱的呢喃。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_nest_narrativeDescription","text":"菌絲體遍布整個賈達密——有時看不見，卻總在竊竊私語。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_egg_name","text":"鳳凰蛋"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_egg_description","text":"某種東西阻止了鳳凰重生。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_phoenix_egg_narrativeDescription","text":"火焰應燃起之處卻一片死寂。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_tomb_name","text":"古怪紀念碑"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_tomb_description","text":"這座雕像給人一種奇怪的感覺，好像不屬於這裡一樣。"},
{"sid":"campaign_M9_tomb_narrativeDescription","text":"如果你擇日再訪……你會發現其他東西。無法擺脫這樣的感覺。"}
] }